Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.23,0:00:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hi, everyone, Kaleido Star is about to start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.02,0:00:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star,\Nplease keep your room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can, okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.48,0:00:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Have any of you ever told the\Nperson you love how you feel?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.31,0:00:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I love you." Like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.19,0:00:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, it makes you so shy, doesn't it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.56,0:00:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Actually, Mr. Policeman says\Nhe's decided to propose to Miss Kate!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That Mr. Policeman. He may look a little scary,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.18,0:00:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but even he gets nervous\Nwhen push comes to shove.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.15,0:00:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Have courage! It's all about guts! Right, Ken?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.65,0:00:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh, you look kinda down... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:01:02.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss, the beginning\Nis red and black passions{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.40,0:01:09.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometimes, we rely on our contrary hearts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:16.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss, the last resort is a\Nmission which changes the future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.85,0:01:24.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is no place for\Nambiguous answers in love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.90,0:01:32.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even while pretending not to\Nsee the impossible reality, we bet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:38.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hard-to-obtain-truth\NCan you feel me now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.23,0:01:42.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I say to myself,\Nwho gets excited easily?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.31,0:01:46.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm confused about what to say {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:55.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dreamin' the never-waking\Ndream, the falling fate{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:02:02.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't stop lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NYa ya ya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.52,0:02:10.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I believe in you, even\Nif I lose everything for it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.35,0:02:17.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NNo no no{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:23.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.23,0:02:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I told you to become my partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.31,0:02:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.93,0:02:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Leon, please stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the one who can become my partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.94,0:02:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sophie! Sophie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Leon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.77,0:03:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sophie... I'm so glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.27,0:03:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Leon has another side to him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's different than the\Ncold side he always shows.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.94,0:03:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's warm... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And sad... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Mr. Leon is someone who fights.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.02,0:03:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've decided not to fight onstage anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I can't become his partner. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.90,0:03:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The path I'm trying to walk is different\Nfrom Mr. Leon's and from Miss Layla's.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's mine and mine alone. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday when I can get back to the stage,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}my goal is a stage with no battling,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}where the audience and\Nthe performers are all smiling.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.35,0:03:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's the kind of\NKaleido Stage I want to create.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.98,0:03:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Mr. Policeman's Amazing Proposal."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.85,0:04:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.65,0:04:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured something like this would\Nhappen, so I brought something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan, get it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Perfect Dating Manual:\N100 Ways To Captivate Her Heart!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to have\NSora stolen from you by Leon,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.52,0:04:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then captivate her, even if\Nyou have to use that book. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.56,0:04:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captivate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:29.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, that looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing that doesn't make me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, if she sees me in this and\Nthinks I've teamed up with Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be fun too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.35,0:04:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When she's in trouble, that's your chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While you tenderly take care of her,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,take advantage of her confusion\Nand invite her out on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.73,0:04:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then take her to a nice, extravagant lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.19,0:04:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then her heart is totally unguarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey guys, let's set high hopes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Ken can't hope for much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:05:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least make Sora feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for always helping me, Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.23,0:05:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is not my boyfriend\Nor anything at all like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it you wanted to talk about, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken, I didn't see you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men need to have guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Women need to have guts too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this world, it's about guts!\NSo get out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora! What's wrong? Did you hit\Nyour head anywhere or anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When she's in trouble, that's your chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This isn't the time for that. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't looking where I was\Nwalking and I bumped into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going on a hospital visit too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it doesn't look like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I was waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if maybe\Nyou'd have lunch with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.73,0:05:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.27,0:05:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could Ken be trying to cheer me up?\NWearing that silly suit, even?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come to think of it, I've done\Nnothing lately but worry everyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay, in that case I'll have so\Nmuch fun that I'll surprise Ken!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ken! I was just getting hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.27,0:06:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.52,0:06:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That outfit looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really! Are you going to team up with Anna?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go change now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that a success?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's follow them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.15,0:06:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a really good restaurant.\NAnd the view from the terrace is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just there last week\Nwith a friend from middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.19,0:06:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, if we turn at this corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.56,0:06:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a... laundromat that's been shut down...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.69,0:06:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we turn that corner on the other end...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there's a bowling alley\Nthat's been shut down,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:07:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and if we turn this corner up here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there's the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we ended up here because...\Nthere are complex reasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the map in that book is wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be! Papa got Mama by using that book!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many years ago was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was before I was born,\Nso I can't really tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ken's started to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's turning to the manual for help...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At times like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.52,0:07:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In unexpected situations,\Nmake the appropriate decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.65,0:07:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the restaurant you're\Ngoing to has been closed down,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,remember whether there's\Nanother restaurant you know close by!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.23,0:07:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the power of love\Nthat we call the fighting spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora? Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora?! Sora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this job was too much for Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.06,0:07:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.77,0:07:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.52,0:07:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a hot dog stand over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.65,0:07:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, want to have hot dogs then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see a terrace, but\Nthere's a good view of the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's a great view.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the weather's nice,\Nhanging out outside is the best, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.23,0:08:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for inviting me, Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.98,0:08:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu'h wegkome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.94,0:08:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's the point of me {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.17,0:08:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}getting cheered up by her?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am a man, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.40,0:08:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to take the lead! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.68,0:08:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is nice weather, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it feels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice weather...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.27,0:08:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just need a little more courage...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Mr. Policeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Policeman!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora... Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Policeman, don't take dangerous\Nshortcuts when you're in a hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, I'm begging you! Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:08:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Policeman?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to propose to Miss Kate?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Making a romantic\Nproposal by my thirtieth birthday
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has been my dream ever since I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.23,0:09:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you think "What if I ask\Nher and she dodges the question?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you get so you just can't say the words.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you understand me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.73,0:09:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I feel your pain as if it were mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, when is your thirtieth\Nbirthday, Mr. Policeman?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, it's today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you have to hurry\Nup and go see Miss Kate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.81,0:09:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's on vacation from the\Nhospital and she's not at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.44,0:09:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I've got the day off too,\Nand I can't even see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this just means that\Ndreams are better off staying dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Policeman...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Dreams are better off staying dreams."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, we have dreams so they can come true!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We do whatever we can to make that happen!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Policeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Mr. Policeman.\NLet's go make your dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's kind of a strange turn of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.85,0:10:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's okay, because it\Nlooks like Sora's feeling better!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, we have to find Miss Kate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.31,0:10:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we can find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes if your timing is bad,\Notherwise easy things go badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's hopeless after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.90,0:10:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't be pessimistic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chance will definitely come!\NYou have to believe that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like Sora says!\NWhat good will it do for me to lose heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chance will come for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't that Miss Kate?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.90,0:10:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Kate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.23,0:10:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you waiting long, Roberto?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.31,0:10:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like I've got no chance of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With men,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's really not about looks or brains or money...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah! Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's about warmth and sincerity!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.52,0:10:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Miss Kate knows
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:10:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all about your good points!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.10,0:11:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'll go find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.94,0:11:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, what do you mean, "find out"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.94,0:11:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is a dream that won't be\Nfulfilled, maybe I'd rather wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.81,0:11:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'd like to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are we going to keep doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.73,0:11:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I like the way you're doing it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about laughing with your\Nfeelings bursting out like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember how\Nthe audience looked at you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when you were on the\Nstage with Leon and Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is going to take longer than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.19,0:11:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is supposed to be special training?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a new kind of performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.44,0:11:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's a TV shoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or just some weirdoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.40,0:11:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Might be best not to make eye contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is getting more and more complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be careful not to let\Nthem find out who we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.15,0:12:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone finds out,\NI won't be able to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.53,0:12:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Roberto's only a colleague.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just went shopping with me today, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.77,0:12:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.35,0:12:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I had something I wanted to ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I didn't eat a whole meal before...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, let's go eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's payday, so I'll treat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.48,0:12:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go to the bank\Nfor a second, so come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I have to tell\NMr. Policeman he can rest easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what she's trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My unease only grows.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.19,0:12:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's it doing that at this time of day?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.48,0:12:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a bad feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be a bank robbery, could it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand over the money quietly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me.\NI'm the unluckiest man in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerry?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Policeman! Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Policeman? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really. Now, let go of Kate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.77,0:13:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, my first bank robbery\Never and there's a policeman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really am the unluckiest man in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys! Now you get that\NI'm telling the truth, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody on the second floor,\Nyou come down here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you, tie the policeman up with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.15,0:13:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tie him tightly. I'm gonna\Ncheck up on you afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's not enough rope,\Nthere's plenty more in my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Preparation is the one thing I'm good at.\NMy grandma always praised me for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Mr. Policeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we pull any stupid tricks,\Nyou'll be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can tie it tightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.27,0:14:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a patrol car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you guys contact the police you'll be sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man, am I closing the barn door too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they don't report everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the inside of this bank is set up\Nso it can be constantly monitored.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just what you'd expect from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.02,0:14:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really am the unluckiest man in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it really is a bank robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention, criminal! Release the\Nhostages quietly and come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.48,0:14:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything that happens in there\Nis being watched on our monitors!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like all of the hostages are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.02,0:14:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stop now, your crimes are still light.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might be dissatisfied about\Nsome things in this world, but so are we!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.02,0:14:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.19,0:14:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how little pocket money
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.36,0:14:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my wife lets me have each day?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:14:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:15:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a number I can say in front of people!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:15:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora and Ken are both okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world's full of phonies!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always at a disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.02,0:15:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was supposed to\Nstop feeling like that today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted money to make my dream come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.27,0:15:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't have to be a fortune.\NMy dream's a small one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to a country with a low\Ncost of living and no phonies,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,meet a woman who\Ndoesn't call me a blockhead,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.77,0:15:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and get hold of a little bit of happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.48,0:15:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't a tiny dream\Nlike that come true?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it me?! Is it my fault?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.19,0:15:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it look like it'll come true?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll come true. I'll make it come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty sure of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of a dream is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.23,0:15:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To create a Kaleido Stage\Nwhere everyone can smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.77,0:15:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you one of the Kaleido Stage cast?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a phony show!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phony?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by phony?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kaleido Stage isn't phony!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're from Kaleido Stage too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna get taken in by phonies anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to doubt everything that's\Nunbelievable and live life on the winning side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe anything\NI don't see with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.23,0:16:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been reborn as a man with a heart of steel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a performance here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here and now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, now's not the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.06,0:16:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking to this girl about dreams right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't butt in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.27,0:16:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said your dream was to\Nmake everyone smile, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.40,0:16:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then make me smile.\NMe, the man with the steel heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.31,0:16:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:16:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm borrowing your rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:16:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, please sit back\Nand watch through to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.19,0:17:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.02,0:17:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and what do you think my\Ndaughter's boyfriend called me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...doing a show.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see! I wanna see!\NI wanna see! I wanna see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see! I wanna see!\NI wanna see! I wanna see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Mia, which bank is it?\NI have to hurry or it'll be over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're done?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.81,0:17:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.40,0:17:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been coming here every\Nday lately, so I figured you might be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mia called me and said Sora's\Ndoing a police drama at a bank
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and it's on TV and they're shooting right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, wanna go watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell what she's talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if we go we'll figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.52,0:17:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in doing\Nany more today anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.19,0:18:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait! I'll keep trying! Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.06,0:18:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You come too, May!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm so sorry, thank you so\Nmuch for driving me there too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That really wasn't my intention\Nwhen I told you about it, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, the more the merrier.\NAlthough it's a bit cramped.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right now, this is my stage. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.81,0:18:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the people who are watching me,\Nand for that man, I'll give it my all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really not rigged?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone's made me remember\Nwhat it feels like to be the audience.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}More than the amazing performances,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it was the way everyone onstage\Nlooked like they had so much fun{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.02,0:18:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that was the biggest reason\NI fell in love with Kaleido Stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After I understood that my mom\Nand dad weren't ever coming back,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}somehow before I knew it I was\Nalways thinking about Kaleido Stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was because I felt\Nlike if I went to Kaleido Stage,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.06,0:19:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I could have fun again like I did that time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.98,0:19:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just smiled, didn't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Sora won this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why Sora worked so hard for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, one reason was to\Nprove that Kaleido Stage isn't phony.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.69,0:19:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the other one was that Sora\Nwants you to get your smile back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.98,0:19:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wants all the people\Nwho watch her show to smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and all the people who\Nperform onstage with her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I want to create a Kaleido Stage
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:20:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where the audience and\Nthe cast can all have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like it when people smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.19,0:20:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, that's a tough dream to make\Nhappen, but Sora thinks she can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she works so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For her dream, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've decided to try\Nworking a little for my dream too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to propose to that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.40,0:20:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dream's as small as yours, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine isn't a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just a loser looking for place to escape to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start all over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.04,0:20:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's what I'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it. I'll leave by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.60,0:20:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the one you really have to catch, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You can stop, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.94,0:20:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I take back what I said\Nabout it being phony. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.56,0:20:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.19,0:21:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, please come to\Nsee the show at Kaleido Stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.90,0:21:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.10,0:21:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over already? What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, it was a good show.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was great, Sora! Yay Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.19,0:21:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora's as great as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It hurts, but her moves were definitely good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And she wasn't even onstage... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.94,0:21:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What does Sora have that I don't have?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.38,0:21:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like back when we were kids, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.73,0:21:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder Kate rescued Crybaby Jerry\Nall the time when he got bullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.02,0:21:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I built up my body because\NI didn't like the way I was then, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerry, your good point is your kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kate...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.49,0:21:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.99,0:21:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to put you under eternal arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.06,0:21:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy thirtieth birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.02,0:22:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll arrest you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.48,0:22:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kate!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.48,0:22:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like right now, the stage is\Nstill the only thing that captivates Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.60,0:22:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What Sagittarius wants...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.81,0:22:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A stage with no battling,\Ncolored only by smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an extremely foolish dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.06,0:22:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's foolish, and therefore\Nit's a path no one dares to walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.06,0:22:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits at the end is either applause...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.46,0:22:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or scorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.60,0:22:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.44,0:22:49.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All kinds of hard luck flocks\Nyour way as if it's spurring you on{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.84,0:22:53.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Swept away by it, time is over {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.98,0:22:56.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just as predicted, take it easy {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:23:01.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will get you out right away {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.27,0:23:02.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hurry up (Here we go) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.98,0:23:04.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forcibly only (Drive with the fastest speed){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.82,0:23:08.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The view I look down at every day is the best{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:10.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sunset point (Favorite) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.65,0:23:12.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Harbor light (Stormy night) {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.37,0:23:16.48,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Escape for the sake of tomorrow {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.15,0:23:22.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even I don't have a vacation, I've got an oasis{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.98,0:23:29.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll turn off the cell phone and charge my love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.94,0:23:34.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because some pain,\Nyou can't soothe with just kindness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:38.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are alone, we pass each other by{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.56,0:23:39.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's going on? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.85,0:23:45.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At the far end of regret,\NI encounter my true heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.40,0:23:53.94,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether I'm crying or\Nlaughing, I will be with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.28,0:23:57.62,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Kaleido Star: New Wings
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.94,0:24:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this feeling springing up inside of me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.75,0:24:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so! In the end,\Neveryone's smiles really are the best!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.52,0:24:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whatever it is Sora's got that I don't...\NIt hurts, but I'll find out what that is for sure!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.09,0:24:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A great performance with\NMay at Mr. Kenneth's event!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.35,0:24:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And... here goes, Rosetta!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.34,0:24:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay, Teacher! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.30,0:24:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time on Kaleido Star,\N"Launching An Amazing Smile!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.65,0:24:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My wings are my dream\Nand on towards the sky...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.23,0:24:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
